      <title>华纳兄弟探索频道任命美国网络业务主管 Channing Dungey 领导下的主要高管</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/warner-bros-discovery-names-key-executives-under-us-networks-business-head-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华纳兄弟探索频道周三任命了其美国网络业务执行团队的主要成员，该业务将由华纳兄弟电视集团董事长兼首席执行官钱宁·邓吉 (Channing Dungey) 领导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/warner-bros-discovery-names-key-executives-under-us-networks-business-head-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 23:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
