      <title>美国监管机构要求 USAA 联邦储蓄银行纠正不安全做法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-regulator-orders-usaa-federal-savings-bank-correct-unsafe-practices-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国货币监理署（OCC）周三表示，USAA联邦储蓄银行已被要求纠正一系列长期存在的监管缺陷，这些缺陷构成了不安全和不健全的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-regulator-orders-usaa-federal-savings-bank-correct-unsafe-practices-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:08:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
