      <title>英国监管机构称 Direct Line 违反了保险附加条款规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-watchdog-says-direct-line-breached-rules-over-insurance-add-on-2024-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国竞争监管机构周三表示，Direct Line 违反了命令，在未经客户许可的情况下错误地在客户保单中增加了“无索赔奖金保护”附加条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-watchdog-says-direct-line-breached-rules-over-insurance-add-on-2024-12-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 11:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
